{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 67,
  "title": "第六十七章（三寶）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天下皆謂我大 不宵 夫唯大 故不宵 若宵 細久矣"
    },
    {
      "text": "我恆有三寶之 一曰茲 二曰檢 三曰不敢為天下先"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫茲 故能勇 檢 故能廣 不敢為天下先 故能為成事長"
    },
    {
      "text": "今捨亓茲且勇 捨亓檢且廣 捨亓後且先 則必死矣"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫茲 以戰則勝 以守則固 天將建之 如以茲垣之"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言：天下謂我德大，我則佯愚似不肖。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯獨名德大者為身害，故佯愚似若不肖。無所分別，無所割截，不賤人而自貴。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "肖，善也。謂辨惠也。若大辨惠之人，身高自貴行察察之政所從來久矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言辨惠者唯如小人，非長者。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言：我有三寶，抱持而保倚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "愛百姓若赤子。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "賦歛若取之於己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 15,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "執謙退，不為倡始也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以慈仁，故能勇於忠孝也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天子身能節儉，故民日用廣矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不為天下首先。故能成器長。成器長，謂得道人也。我能為得道人之長也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "今世人捨慈仁，但為勇武。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "捨其儉約，但為奢泰。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "捨其後己，但為人先。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "所行如此，動入死地。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫慈仁者，百姓親附，並心一意，故以戰則勝敵，以守衛則堅固。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天將救助善人，必與慈仁之性，使能自營助也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "久矣其細，猶曰其細久矣。肖，則失其所以為大矣。故曰，若肖久矣，其細也夫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫慈，以陳則勝，以守則固，故能勇也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "節儉愛費，天下不匱，故能廣也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯後外其身，為物所歸，然後乃能立成器為天下利，為物之長也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "且，猶取也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "相慜而不避於難，故勝也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
